    LocaleSelector, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class LocaleSelectorImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements LocaleSelector
    An implementation of the model object 'Locale Selector'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Loc Flgs
    • Lang Code
    • Scrpt Cde
    • Reg Cde
    • Reserved
    • Var Cde
